#install/perception/bin/detector_basic
#This executes the DetectorBasic node defined in perception/detector_basic.py, which:

#Subscribes to /limo/depth_camera_link/image_raw.

#Converts images via CvBridge.

#Thresholds red pixels, finds contours, and computes bounding boxes.

#Publishes PolygonStamped messages on /object_polygon.

#Shows colour image and detection mask windows via OpenCV.​​

#5. Verify detection output
#Optional checks in additional terminals:

#Confirm the node is running:

#bash
#ros2 node list
# should include /detector_basic
#Confirm image traffic:

#bash
#ros2 topic echo /limo/depth_camera_link/image_raw --once
#Confirm detections:

#bash
#ros2 topic echo /object_polygon
